      "comment_id" : 119133277,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@saran3h That means that you haven&#39;t overridden <code>equals(Object)</code> in that class. See also <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/22658385/why-this-two-simple-objects-are-not-equal\">Why this two simple objects are not equal?</a>"
